data.description: POOL HOME!!!  3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom block home in College Park! Escape to your personal backyard and pool area. Large storage area and laundry room. 3rd bedroom can be in-law suite with bathroom, kitchen or can be a caterers/chef kitchen with large pantry. Home is connected with natural gas for generator, kitchen stove and other appliances. Lovely screened front porch. Crown moldings in bedrooms. Close to beach, downtown WPB and Lake Worth. Priced to sell and ready for your personal touches. A must see!!
